import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Fotter from '../components/Fotter'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar'
import Newsletter from '../components/Newsletter'
import { Notification } from '../components/Notification'


const Container= styled.div`
    
`
const Product = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
       <Navbar/>
       <Notification/>
       <Wrapper>
        <ImageContainer>
            <Image src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/20/45/89/20458914e7e373c2cecb72e6760dadda.jpg"/>
        </ImageContainer>
        <InfoContainer>
            <Title>T-Shirt</Title>
            <Desc>One of few designs with a front and back logo. This popular shark crunch over Muscle beach is perfect for any occasion.

Custom Muscle Beach neck tag
Super soft Spectra Spun ring-spun 100% cotton perfection fabric
Unisex
100% NAFTA compliant</Desc>
            <Price> RS.1,500</Price>
        </InfoContainer>
       </Wrapper>
       <Newsletter/>
       <Fotter/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Product
